      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — 5 operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted velocity magnitudes compared against 2023 PIV data at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error across planes is 4.2% of peak velocity. Acceptable for flow-field validation; hemolysis scalar validation remains limited by stale calibration data."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/hemolysis-index-bench-2023",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Hemolysis index bench comparison — 3 operating points",
      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at 3 operating points. Agreement within 18% at best operating point; model systematically under-predicts at high shear conditions, consistent with stale 2018 calibration constants not reflecting revised turbulence model."
    }
  ],
