      "rationale": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed on 12 model inputs including hemolysis exponent C and alpha. However, the distributions for C and alpha are derived from the 2018 calibration dataset, which predates the January 2026 model revision. No re-calibration was performed after the turbulence coupling was revised. Input uncertainty is therefore underestimated for the current model build. Achieved level 2 against required level 4.",
